data.description: Discover the perfect blend of New Mexico nature and convenience on this stunning 15-acre lot, just 20 minutes from Santa Fe. Enjoy the breathtaking views of the Sangre de Cristos, Jemez and Sandia mountains...sunsets and sunrises included. Bring your horses and your plans to build your dream equestrian property with space for 3 horses on this nearly 15 acre parcel. Reasonable covenants, paved roads and access to electric and natural gas. Water is through Eldorado Community and requires a private meter. Eldorado amenities are nearby. Schedule your showing today.
